      • moveToNext

        boolean moveToNext​(FeatureDataSource.Content.ContentPointer pointer)
        Increments the specified content pointer. When the FeatureDataSource.Content.ContentPointer.FEATURE_SET pointer is incremented the the FeatureDataSource.Content.ContentPointer.FEATURE pointer is automatically reset to the first feature for the new set.
        Parameters:
        pointer - The pointer to be incremented
        Returns:
        true if there is another feature, false if no more features are available.
